zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3）今日在長洲廣傳的擬似冒警照片，經查證後是警察學校在長洲進行訓練。</span>1925hrs<br />\n<br />\n離島區議員   鄺官穩"},{"pid":"19f620923e23f9889784de9c6126fb24ed969277","tid":1512622,"uid":154429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"警察都有得扮？ 如果有得扮，企前線就全部都警察啦。"},{"pid":"63e13fbe63a64b737e9d8002b0a494ac8c78a001","tid":1512622,"uid":210140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"258df9bcbf82dd44138d3abd024bb82d31551136","tid":1512622,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLk3Kce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLk3Kce.jpg&h=3fd9d2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/go5Lc5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgo5Lc5A.jpg&h=7eb4acfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人幫手解釋下，係咪拍戲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"圖二女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4356eb27967c76fb35ea7c1634f6f8442fc7eede","tid":1512622,"uid":208095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"仆街班人傳g鋒係長洲搞緊臨時政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b3a5cbe5078e50c6bd8b5275e7d9a38f10b3dd","tid":1512622,"uid":233453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"我建議中國這樣懲罰香港：<br />\n1. 不准香港加入大灣區，等香港沒得分享當大灣區人的榮耀<br />\n2. 不准香港建三跑，人工島，使香港少了未來發展方向<br />\n3. 停止每日 150 殖民，令香港人口老化<br />\n3.5 與中國人通婚之港人，其香港藉改為中國藉，需申請簽證才可去香港，吸走香港的勞動力<br />\n4. 停東江水，令香港被迫另求水源建海水化淡廠<br />\n5. 撤走駐港解放軍，使美軍攻擊香港時的沒人保衛香港<br />\n6. 要求所有中國教職員和優才辭職，返中國工作，貢獻自己才能知識、唔益香港人，你以為搞科研就請回香港人<br />\n7. 將工聯會撤回中國，香港不配有那麼好的工會，等你班人無得學中國象棋<br />\n8. 在香港買奶粉回國，一律無期徙刑，等你香港人無得賺奶粉錢<br />\n9. 不再委任特首，等你自己選，以後特首級人才留給你慢慢用<br />\n10. 不教普通話與簡體字，香港人永遠學不會講不好中國的文明語言與規範文字，被中國人當醜小鴨排斥<br />\n11.強制所有中國國民即日撤走香港所有資產，規定包括不可持有任何香港物業、不可擔任公司股東、不可持有任何香港銀行之戶口、不可進行任何融資，違反者將會&rsquo;立即送中&rsquo;，回國後即判無期徙刑"},{"pid":"2847d7cf19d55676f4125a277e82dfe70af47f16","tid":1512622,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"〔過牆梯〕淆底唔敢入機場既同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512735</a>"},{"pid":"174193593d9a5dbcd5bc1c74c5bf7c8ff2ecc084","tid":1512622,"uid":7835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"除咗長洲之外<br />\n我仲聽過山頂球場秘密練兵呢個講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e8a06001a965ce7217e7381a1b804d783be286","tid":1512622,"uid":190043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"Holy shit<br />\n佢哋個腦真係攞黎裝屎架<br />\n解乜9釋<br />\n咪用d濕9藉口屈9我哋<br />\n跟撚住又抄晒車<br />\nCCTVB:狗方表示長州有狗賊進行演習/<br />\n             本台拍攝新劇"},{"pid":"9d30b165b397a30997aef162d517b26e2fad8a72","tid":1512622,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"自己唔報警，叫人廣傳去叫警察做野<br />\n但都有弱智會信"},{"pid":"7019e7a27802ac5c4691ba088496d92a42e9af9e","tid":1512622,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c632274db5330a50db11085fde1b3fc07d323b1d","tid":1512622,"uid":269216,"like":46,"dislike":8,"score":38,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"條腿好白好直<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T0